  "plan": "## ConsensusClustering GenePattern Module — Implementation Plan\n\n### 1. Overview\nConsensusClustering is a GenePattern module that Resampling-based clustering method\n\n### 2. Parameters\nThe module exposes 15 parameters:\n- Required: input.filename, kmax, resampling.iterations, output.stub\n- Optional: seed.value, clustering.algorithm, cluster.by, distance.measure, resample, merge.type, descent.iterations, normalize.type, normalization.iterations, create.heat.map, heat.map.size\n\n### 3. Command Line\n```\n<run-with-env> -u Java -u R-2.5 java <java_flags> -cp <libdir>Acme.jar<path.separator><libdir>gp-modules.jar<path.separator><libdir>broad-cg.jar<path.separator><libdir>geneweaver.jar<path.separator><libdir>RunSomAlg.jar<path.separator><libdir>jaxb-rt-1.0-ea.jar<path.separator><libdir>file_support.jar<path.separator><libdir>archiver.jar<path.separator><libdir>trove.jar<path.separator><libdir>gp-common.jar<path.separator><libdir>Jama-1.0.2.jar<path.separator><libdir>cc.jar edu.mit.broad.modules.cc.CC <input.filename> <kmax> <resampling.iterations> <normalize.type> -N <normalization.iterations> -@<seed.value> -S <resample> -t <clustering.algorithm> <cluster.by> -D <distance.measure> -L <merge.type> -i <descent.iterations> -o <output.stub> -s -d <create.heat.map> -z <heat.map.size> -l0 -v0 -b<libdir>\n```\n\n### 4. Docker Image\nDocker image: \n\n### 5. Validation Strategy\n- Validate all required parameters are provided\n- Validate file formats match expected extensions\n- Check parameter value ranges where applicable\n\n### 6. Implementation Roadmap\nPhase 1: Wrapper script implementation\nPhase 2: Docker container setup\nPhase 3: Parameter validation and error handling\nPhase 4: Testing and documentation",
  "wrapper_script": "Acme.jar<path.separator><libdir>gp-modules.jar<path.separator><libdir>broad-cg.jar<path.separator><libdir>geneweaver.jar<path.separator><libdir>RunSomAlg.jar<path.separator><libdir>jaxb-rt-1.0-ea.jar<path.separator><libdir>file_support.jar<path.separator><libdir>archiver.jar<path.separator><libdir>trove.jar<path.separator><libdir>gp-common.jar<path.separator><libdir>Jama-1.0.2.jar<path.separator><libdir>cc.jar",
